---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About Vaughn" 
  description="Meet Vaughn Sterling - your personal guide to South Africa's hidden treasures. Cape Town local with years of hospitality experience."
>
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-navy mb-6">
          About <span class="text-gold">Vaughn</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          Your personal guide to South Africa's hidden treasures
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Profile Section -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden mb-12">
        <div class="md:flex">
          <div class="md:w-2/5">
            <img 
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=600&h=800&fit=crop"
              alt="Vaughn Sterling"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-3/5 p-8 md:p-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">
              Welcome to My World
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              <p>
                I'm Vaughn Sterling, and South Africa isn't just where I live—it's my passion, 
                my home, and the place I want to share with you in the most authentic way possible.
              </p>
              <p>
                For years, I've been welcoming international guests to Cape Town, showing them 
                not the tourist traps, but the real South Africa. The wine estate where the 
                owner will personally pour for you. The restaurant where locals celebrate. 
                The sunset spot that isn't in any guidebook.
              </p>
              <p>
                What started as showing friends around has evolved into something special: 
                creating bespoke experiences that go beyond typical tours. This is about 
                connection, authenticity, and creating memories that last a lifetime.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Why Different -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-navy to-sa-blue p-8 rounded-2xl text-white">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gold">Why I'm Different</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-100">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-gold text-xl">•</span>
              <span>This is personal, not transactional. You're not a client, you're a guest.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-gold text-xl">•</span>
              <span>I live here. These aren't scripted facts—they're my favorite places.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-gold text-xl">•</span>
              <span>Discretion is paramount. Your privacy is my priority.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-gold text-xl">•</span>
              <span>Flexible and spontaneous. If you want to change plans, we change plans.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border-2 border-gold">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-navy">What I Bring</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Local Knowledge:</strong> Born and raised in South Africa</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Hospitality Experience:</strong> Years of welcoming international guests</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Cultural Insight:</strong> I bridge cultures and translate nuances</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Professional Network:</strong> Access to exclusive venues</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Personal Philosophy -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gold to-sa-gold p-8 md:p-12 rounded-2xl text-center">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">My Philosophy</h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-navy/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed italic">
          "Travel isn't about checking boxes. It's about connection, discovery, and those 
          unexpected moments that become your favorite stories. That's what I create for you."
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-navy">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Ready to Explore Together?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 mb-8">Let's create your perfect South African experience</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-gold to-sa-gold text-navy font-bold rounded-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all">
        Get in Touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
